content: round 49 before treble_crochet single_crochet in same ch2 space 3sc in treble_crochet single_crochet in next ch2 space 6dctog in corner space of round 49 after treble_crochet single_crochet in same ch2 space single_crochet in next double_crochet single_crochet in ch2 space 6dctog2 in the 2 skipped sts of round 49 single_crochet in same ch2 space single_crochet in next double_crochet repeat 63x in the 4th chain 2sc s y b u l hint the skipped st is always a 6dctog2 or a 6dctog 52 ch2 2sc in first st single_crochet in next 3sts skip 1 sts repeat until 5sc corner single_crochet in the next 2 sts 3sc in next st single_crochet in the next 2sts skip next st single_crochet in next 3 sts repeat until 1 st left 2 single_crochet in the last st cut your yarn and work away all of the ends if you have any questions need help making this pattern or just want to show your results join the facebook group lubys crochet corner i would love to see your results love lubys copyright lubys eva numan all rights reserved this pattern is for personal use only you do not have the right to claim this pattern as your own nor to sell the pattern or share the file in any form you have no right to make video tutorials of this pattern you may sell your finished item but you may not use my pictures to promote the item
